Class BinaryTree<T>

java.lang.Object
src.BinaryTree<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
BinaryTreeInterface<T>, TreeInterface<T>
public class BinaryTree<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements BinaryTreeInterface<T>
A class of trees whose entries are stored in binary nodes in which each node has at most two children.
